name: New Sheetal Pure Veg Restaurant

reviews.review_text: One of the best restaurant for Vegetarian food. Preparations are really very good and ambience is also perfect. Staff is very helpful and polite in nature. I am satisfied with food and the service of staff. Rates are reasonable and two wheelers parking is available. 4 vehicles can be parked on the opposite side of the road.

Great Deluxe Punjabi Thali

The Deluxe Punjabi Thali is an excellent option here.

It costs Rs 260 and is very filling.

The thali covers almost everything from soup to dessert.

You should definitely try it once!

With tags like "thali" (49 mentions), "value" (18 mentions), "beach" (15 mentions), and "north Indian food" (13 mentions) echoing through customer feedback, this restaurant promises a flavorful experience that caters to veg enthusiasts.
